    body
        h1 3axes
        hr
        button(class="button", onclick="location.href='instructions'", style="font-size:36pt") Click here to start!

        h2 What is 3axes?
        p 3axes is a political quiz that attempts to assign percentages for three political axes. You will be presented by a statement, and then you will answer with your opinion on the statement, from <b>Strongly Agree</b> to <b>Strongly Disagree</b>, with each answer slightly affecting your scores. At the end of the quiz, your answers will be compared to the maximum possible for each value, thus giving you a percentage. Answer honestly!
        <p>There are <b><u><span id="numOfQuestions"></span></u></b> questions.</p>
        br
        h2 What are the three axes?
        p In-group, Property, and Society - and each has two opposing values assigned to them.
        br
        
        <p class="value-description"><b style="color:#0000ff;">Tribal</b> (In-group)<br/>
            div Those with higher Individual scores are more nationalistic or individualistic.</p>
        <p class="value-description"><b style="color:#ffff00;">Global</b> (In-group)<br/>
            div Those with higher Global scores are cosmopolitan and globalist.</p>
        <br>
        <p class="value-description"><b style="color:#ff0000;">Private</b> (Property)<br/>
            div Those with higher Private scores believe in personal liberties and responsibility.</p>
        <p class="value-description"><b style="color:#00ffff;">Collective</b> (Property)<br/>
            div Those with higher Collective scores believe in state power and wealth redistribution.</p>
        <br>
        <p class="value-description"><b style="color:#00ff00;">Hierarchy</b> (Society)<br/>
            div Those with higher Hierarchy scores believe in cultural homogeneity and adherence to a moral code.</p>
        <p class="value-description"><b style="color:#ff00ff;">Equality</b> (Society)<br/>
            div Those with higher Equality scores believe in cultural change and equality.</p>
        <br>

